VERSION: 0.1.0

REQUERIMENTS
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 * python-django-tinymce A django module to integrate tinymce WYSIWYG editor.
 * python-django-south
 * gettext
 * django-admin-tools --> https://bitbucket.org/izi/django-admin-tools/
 * python-feedparser 
 * django-fluent-dashboard --> https://github.com/edoburu/django-fluent-dashboard
 * django-rosetta
 
INSTALLATION
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

0. Install the requeriments
1. Synchronize the data base:

 $ ./manage.py syncdb
 $ ./manage.py migrate web 
 $ ./manage.py migrate admin_tools.dashboard
 $ ./manage.py migrate admin_tools.menu

2. Load default data:

 $ ./manage.py loaddata

INTERNATIONALIZATION
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. To generate the .po files to translate:

 $ ./manage.py makemessages -l <language>

<language> = es for Spanish.

2. Edit the .po file in locale/es/LC_MESSAGES/ and translate.

3. To generate the .mo file:

 $ ./manage.py compilemessages

